column4: NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "326CC1AC4DDE0731909895B68E248514", "Light skills focus the fading light of day into single target or piercing ranged attacks. Use light skills to buff your attacks or avoid damage.The Light buff boosts Mana regen.")

NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "87D2ABD642836679B217A78958D7347A", "Dark skills harness the gathering darkness to hurl dark bolts at many targets. Use dark skills to debuff or slow your enemies.The Dark buff increases damage.")

NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "740EB9DF477F67444526B79A6BA978B6", "The rich history of the Railmasters endures while you practice your Slammer skills. Wield your rail tools, including your trusty Railhammer, against foes.Your fortitude gives you a defensive bonus while using melee skills.")

NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "CA25ED544DA8F3CB7430DDA6B94F9F0E", "Conductor skills are all about your battle train. These skills let you customize its cars and unleash its powerful attacks in battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "C4BC47BB447164F6BE772E92263B9060", "Brawl skills make the Forged a formidable close-range melee fighter, protected by a defensive bonus while using melee skills.")
NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "2E7493EC4639441AC23F4EAC5FC269F5", "Barrage skills utilize the Forged\'s chest cannon to attack from a distance.")

column15: Mostly here to help keep the code clean and select the no ember weapon tab

column9: NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "F467041448BFDC99FA2A8D8B764B3F53", "A spider bite is an annoyance, thousands however...")

column4: NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "550C466E46116230C252ACA60B7F1602", "Take aim with Precision skills, deftly firing on enemies with various ranged shots.Precision skills consume ammo.")

NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "A5D62B674574385C92430694A5F0FE25", "Adventurer skills use artifacts the Sharpshooter has collected to debuff enemies.Each Adventurer skill gives an Adventurer\'s Bonus buff that applies to the next 3 Precision skills.")

NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "D46D6DD7474FDB46BA6B4893CABC9784", "Show your enemies a shocking good time. ")
NSLOCTEXT("SkillsTabTable", "7CDD2F1141518F385E4920BB08450713", "Wore by the greatest, now passed onto you.")
